| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3521 — Recovery Inhibition (nokoyawa)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: cb8841ef-7c7d-51c4-b05e-edb5e3232887"
